body:
Hello avicus,
I'm just popping by to see if anyone still remembers me.

I used to be one of the biggest avicus youtubers,
I used to be one of the avicus staff members,
I used to be really well known among avicus members.

I have seen that the staff have changed dramatically, and I only know 1 or 2 of them.

So, does anyone still know who i am?
-Sean

*for any of you that have steam, here is my account link: http://steamcommunity.com/id/SeanCSGO
*make sure to post a comment like "im from avicus"
